{"tid":934583,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"【挑戰《復仇者3》？】《水行俠》大陸票房三日收5.4億 積遜拍片多謝中國","createTime":"2018-12-09T11:30:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-09T14:48:41.000Z","uid":212399,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3b423f17f92678663894bdd0750e50dd8889ed1b","tid":934583,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:30:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181209/large/1544348575_a36c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181209%2Flarge%2F1544348575_a36c.jpg&h=92dab503&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nDC英雄片大作《水行俠》（Aquaman），破天荒率先比美國早兩星期於中國上畫。而於大陸上映3日，電影票房已達到5.4億人民幣。為答謝觀眾，積遜莫瑪（Jason Momoa）專程拍片，表示：「你好，中國！我只係想講我有幾感激，幾個星期前我嚟到中國，我好激動、好開心電影於中國反應咁好，希望好快同大家再見！」<br />\n雖然《水行俠》開畫票房不及不久前上映嘅《毒魔》（Venom），但以《水行俠》聲勢，要破《毒魔》第一周7.66億票房其實唔難。而《毒魔》最後於大陸埋單有18.53億票房，Marvel大作《復仇者聯盟3：無限之戰》（Avengers: Infinity War）就收23.9億人民幣，唔知《水行俠》會否挑戰到《復仇者3》嘅紀錄？<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181209/59009735\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009735&d=8S8G0peBvkyZaqVbO4V6Cp4f2li5K%2Fs6EGgmwhpeblA%3D&h=29649481\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.entertainment.appledaily.com%2Fenews%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20181209%2F59009735&h=9246f23a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20181209/59009735</a>"},{"pid":"497d2305ab792f4172c023e50588a15948cb9a14","tid":934583,"uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:30:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbadd12d5382e6ba93f59cb23faa6be6320e2487","tid":934583,"uid":52215,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T11:37:24.000Z","msg":"DC發力啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2b6c33a6a3c042be14a48d50440c84f2f01087f","tid":934583,"uid":6026,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:38:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dBMAwmL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdBMAwmL.png&h=1e02c795&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n你好！中國<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eabd3eb592b77aebe0038924f79157b865cc775f","tid":934583,"uid":159183,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T12:58:20.000Z","msg":"好想快d睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ba2dfbb9a41578a3180b4257586545afa836af28","tid":934583,"uid":114692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T14:48:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}